metadata.name: Heavier Is The Head That Wears No Crown
metadata.description:
Heavier Is The Head That Wears No Crown:

When a picket fence says;
“this is worthy of protection”
And having no fence says;
 “you can’t protect what you have”

This is not for the ones with picket fences.
This is for when you want to protect that which is not commonly worthy.
This is for when it is not glittering,
This is for when the grass is any other color but green.
This is not for digiligent men who stand before kings,
For them, crowns matter.
This is for the ones who can not care who is king.

This is the first Installation of my four part genesis collection La Noyade(The Drowing) for SuperRare.
